<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <div class="text-center mb-5">
        <h1 style="font-weight: 700; color: #1d1d1f; font-size: 2.5rem;">로그인</h1>
        <p class="text-muted" style="font-size: 1.1rem;">생산관리 시스템에 오신 것을 환영합니다</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card" style="border: 1px solid #e8e8ed; border-radius: 16px; box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
        <div class="card-body p-5">
          <%= form_for(resource, as: resource_name, url: session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
            <div class="mb-4">
              <%= f.label :email, "이메일", class: "form-label", style: "font-weight: 500; color: #1d1d1f;" %>
              <%= f.email_field :email, autofocus: true, autocomplete: "email", class: "form-control form-control-lg", placeholder: "user@example.com", style: "border-radius: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #d2d2d7;" %>
            </div>

            <div class="mb-4">
              <%= f.label :password, "비밀번호", class: "form-label", style: "font-weight: 500; color: #1d1d1f;" %>
              <%= f.password_field :password, autocomplete: "current-password", class: "form-control form-control-lg", placeholder: "비밀번호를 입력하세요", style: "border-radius: 10px; border: 1.5px solid #d2d2d7;" %>
            </div>

            <% if devise_mapping.rememberable? %>
              <div class="mb-4">
                <div class="form-check">
                  <%= f.check_box :remember_me, class: "form-check-input", style: "cursor: pointer;" %>
                  <%= f.label :remember_me, "로그인 상태 유지", class: "form-check-label", style: "cursor: pointer; color: #6e6e73;" %>
                </div>
              </div>
            <% end %>

            <div class="d-grid mb-4">
              <%= f.submit "로그인", class: "btn-apple btn-apple-primary btn-lg", style: "border-radius: 10px; font-weight: 600; padding: 0.875rem;" %>
            </div>

            <div class="alert alert-info" role="alert" style="border-radius: 10px; background-color: #e3f2fd; border: none;">
              <i class="bi bi-shield-lock me-2"></i>
              <small><strong>보안 안내:</strong> 승인된 디바이스에서만 로그인할 수 있습니다. 새 디바이스는 관리자 승인이 필요합니다.</small>
            </div>
          <% end %>

          <div class="text-center mt-4">
            <%= render "devise/shared/links" %>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <small class="text-muted">
          <i class="bi bi-info-circle me-1"></i>
          문제가 있으신가요? 관리자에게 문의하세요
        </small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
